@fehiepsi Do you want to try working on the task
> Rewrite `Gaussian(x=affine)` as a `Gaussian`

following the ideas in #245 ? If not, I'm happy to do this part to unblock our first release. If so, it might be a nice intro to Funsor and give us insight into how to incorporate structured Gamma priors in Funsor #190, generalizing your Pyro PR https://github.com/pyro-ppl/pyro/pull/2025 .
